product_name: FCS Longboard Series Dolphin Natural Glass Flex Stand Up Paddleboard Fin
long_description: The FCS Longboard Series Dolphin Natural Glass Flex stand up paddleboard fin offers great performance for all-around use. Moderately swept-back shape sheds weeds on flatwater, and narrow tip and fiberglass flex enhance rail-to-rail maneuverability in chop. The FCS Longboard Series Dolphin Natural Glass Flex stand up paddleboard fin weighs approximately 10 oz. Compatible for installation in all US long boxes, found in virtually all stand up paddleboards, with an Allen key screw (Allen key and shims included).
